mask = "24";\n\t\t}\n\t\tvar vals = ipaddr.split(".");\n\n\t\tif (vals.length!=4)\n\t\t\treturn false;\n\n\t\tfor (var i=0; i<4; i++)\n\t\t\tif (!TEMP_IsDigit(vals[i]) || vals[i]>255)\treturn false;\n\n\t\tif (COMM_IPv4NETWORK(ipaddr, mask)!=COMM_IPv4NETWORK(network, mask))\n\t\t\treturn false;\n\n\t\treturn true;\n\t}\n\tfunction TEMP_RulesCount(path, id)\n\t{\n\t\tvar max = mask = "24";\n\t\t}\n\t\tvar vals = ipaddr.split(".");\n\n\t\tif (vals.length!=4)\n\t\t\treturn false;\n\n\t\tfor (var i=0; i<4; i++)\n\t\t\tif (!TEMP_IsDigit(vals[i]) || vals[i]>255)\treturn false;\n\n\t\tif (COMM_IPv4NETWORK(ipaddr, mask)!=COMM_IPv4NETWORK(network, mask))\n\t\t\treturn false;\n\n\t\treturn true;\n\t}\n\tfunction TEMP_RulesCount(path, id)\n\t{\n\t\tvar max =
